****************************************************************

New play store policy for upload App Bundle on play store console

1) Make sure Target API level is 30 in platforms/android/build.gradle file and platforms/android/project.properties file.


2) sudo ionic cordova build --release android


3) sudo keytool -genkey -v -keystore my-release-key.keystore -alias HRMSPlus -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000


4) sudo ionic cordova build android


5) cd platforms/android


6) sudo ./gradlew bundle         (This creates app.aab file which is unsigned)


7) sudo "/usr/lib/jvm/jdk1.8.0_261/bin/jarsigner" -keystore "/home/arvind/Desktop/Ionic/HRMS_PLUS/my-release-key.keystore" "/home/arvind/Desktop/Ionic/HRMS_PLUS/platforms/android/app/build/outputs/bundle/release/app.aab" HRMSPLUS

password : password


and now app.aab file is signed and ready to upload playstore